/\A[\w+\-.]+@[a-z\d\-.]+\.[a-z]+\z/i	full regex
/	start of regex
\A	match start of a string
[\w+\-.]+	at least one word character, plus, hyphen, or dot
@	literal “at sign”
[a-z\d\-.]+	at least one letter, digit, hyphen, or dot
\.	literal dot
[a-z]+	at least one letter
\z	match end of a string
/	end of regex
i	case-insensitive
